- Refactored shared utilities: PaginationDto base class, shared worker profile includes constant,
  assertUserIsActive lifted to assert.util.ts
- Replaced RolesGuard with CASL permission-based authorization (@casl/ability v7);
  all controllers now use @CheckAbility(action, subject) instead of @Roles()
- Refactored shared utilities: PaginationDto base class, shared worker profile
  includes constant, assertUserIsActive lifted to assert.util.ts
- Added dev log instruction and skills reference to CLAUDE.md

---

July 10, 2026

- Fixed bug in admin.service.ts resolveNoShow: passed Booking.workerId as { userId }
  to workerProfile.update, causing P2025 and rolling back the entire transaction;
  corrected to { id: workerId } and simplified helper signature
- Rewrote bookings.service.spec.ts: 21 cases covering full state machine (create,
  accept, reject, start, complete, cancel with strike/suspend, reportNoShow)
- Added bookings.cron.spec.ts: expiry batch, no-op, notification failure tolerance
- Added casl-ability.factory.spec.ts: permission matrix for ADMIN, WORKER, CUSTOMER
- Added casl.guard.spec.ts: public bypass, no-metadata allow, no-user deny,
  permitted allow, ForbiddenException on denial
- Added Postgres-backed e2e infrastructure: docker-compose.test.yml, .env.test,
  jest-e2e.json (globalSetup, setupFiles, runInBand), test/e2e/test-app.ts
  (createTestApp with ThrottlerGuard override, mintToken), test/e2e/db.ts
  (resetDb + fixture factories)
- Added e2e suites: auth-guards, bookings-lifecycle, bookings-expiry, no-show
  (regression for the resolveNoShow bug), verification
- Added GET /admin/users, /admin/workers, /admin/bookings with pagination and
  optional status/role filters; returns { items, total, skip, take }
- Added DELETE /categories/:id (admin-only) for soft-deactivation (isActive=false)

